Kenneth BROWN, Appellant, v. LUCKEN-BACH STEAMSHIP COMPANY, Respondent. No. 241. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. Jan. 20, 1930. Silas B. Axtell, of New York City, for appellant. Kirlin, Campbell, Hickox, Keating & Mc-Grann, of New York City (Vernon S. Jones, of New York City, of counsel), for respondent.

Before MANTON, L. HAND, and MACK, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Order affirmed.
